author: @BirdBird-wr8px
text:
How did you become an army? 

 Three years ago. It will be four years in September.  Well, I was in my beautiful life watching some YouTube videos and was going to turn off the computer  when I saw several recommendations from that group of kids, from Korea. As it wasn't the first time YouTube had done this, almost by accident, I uploaded it.  And I thought they were really funny (they were video montages of Bon Voyage and In the Soop). And I saw one more, then I saw another...and then I researched the songs and discovered "Mic Drop" and I thought that after all they, even had really cool music (this all happened in June/July) . Then came the era of "Dynamite" where I just wanted to fix the names and who's who and then I read several comments about Jin's few lines in the song,  I discovered a video (Tiffhany Mishima) that talked about this issue and where she talked about "Epiphany". I went to listen to this song and after that, I was sure that I would never let go of the group.
